headline: Wells Fargo Notes Q4 2025 Pressure on AJG Margins, Trims Price Target
summary: Arthur J. Gallagher & Co. (NYSE:AJG) is included among the 15 Best Stocks to Buy for the Long Term. Wells Fargo analyst Elyse Greenspan trimmed her outlook on Arthur J. Gallagher & Co.
